snippet.title: DHURANDHAR Trailer Reaction! | Ranveer Singh | Sanjay Dutt | Akshaye Khanna
snippet.description:
Achara, Brandon and Vivan dive into the explosive trailer of Dhurander, a powerhouse Pan-India action spectacle set to redefine mass cinema! Directed with fierce vision and packed with electrifying screen presence, Dhurander brings together an unstoppable blend of high-octane action, gripping drama, and larger-than-life storytelling.

Set against the backdrop of political power, legacy, and rebellion, Dhurander follows a fearless hero rising against corruption, injustice, and a system designed to break him. With thunderous dialogue, intense character moments, and jaw-dropping set pieces, this trailer delivers every bit of the adrenaline fans were waiting for.

snippet.title: Raji: Kaliyuga Official Reveal Trailer | IGN India
snippet.description:
Six years after the original, Raji: Kaliyuga begins as Mahabalasura unleashes Kaliyuga an age where every choice risks unmaking the universe.

This sequel to Raji: An Ancient Epic, makes a huge leap into the Third-Person Action-Adventure genre, also featuring dual Protagonists: control Raji with her divine Trishul and her brother Darsh (Golu from Raji: An Ancient Epic), who commands great arcane power.

Developed by Nodding Heads Games, this cosmic struggle of faith and destiny will determine whether the siblings save the universe or are forced to destroy it to end the conflict.

Raji: Kaliyuga is planned for release on Steam, Epic Store Games, Xbox Series X/S, PlayStation, and Switch 2.

#RajiKaliyuga, #Raji2, #NoddingHeadsGames, #ThirdPersonAction, #IndianMythology, #MadeInIndia, #ARPG, #GameReveal #indiangaming

snippet.title: Banda Ik Marona (Official Video) | Shree Brar | Jasmeen Akhtar | Ronn Sandhu | New Punjabi Songs

Shree Brar presents the Official Music Video of Banda Ik Marona. It is a powerful Punjabi song with a gangsta vibe and emotional feel. The track shows a man who has left his old crime life and is now living clean, but still shares his past and pain with the girl he loves.
With strong lyrics by Shree Brar and soulful vocals by Jasmeen Akhtar, this song brings attitude, emotion, and a catchy hook ‚Äî perfect for Punjabi music fans.

Feel the enchanting charm of Mallika Gandha, the magical melody from Telusu Kada that celebrates love in its purest form. With Thaman S‚Äôs captivating music, Sid Sriram‚Äôs soul-stirring voice, and Krishna Kanth‚Äôs poetic lyrics, this song creates a dreamy world of emotions.
Featuring the beautiful chemistry of Siddu Jonnalagadda and Raashii Khanna, Mallika Gandha is a visual and musical treat that will touch your heart instantly.

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Telugu, Subscribe on the below link
https://youtube.com/TipsTelugu

Vocals - Sid Sriram
